Titolo: Bleach: The Blade of Fate

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Bleach: The Blade of Fate is a 2D fighting game that features the cast of characters from the Bleach anime and manga. The game features Nintendo's Wi-Fi Connection, allowing players to connect and play against players all over the world. The game modes include story mode, arcade mode, VS mode, training mode, challenge mode, and survival mode, time attack mode and Urahara shop. The game's theme song is "Ichirin no Hana" by High and Mighty Color.